en.title: Crown Presidential Directors Hall Of Fame!
en.content:
FusionExcel International would like to congratulate the following Presidential Directors for achieving Crown Presidential Director status for outstanding performance with FE!

To Qualify as a Crown Presidential Director you must:

- Achieve minimum 11 Cycles per month for 6 (six) CONSECUTIVE months within each calendar year.

As a Crown Presidential Director you will enjoy the following Benefits:

 

  1. Special Recognition as a Top Performer on stage with a Special Pin, Certificate & Award
  2. Special Recognition on Crown Presidential Director's Hall of Fame on FE website
  3. Priority Lane at HQ Sales Counter
  4. Priority Lane at HQ Stock Pick Up Counter
  5. Priority Table Booking for FE Functions
  6. Priority Booking of Meeting Rooms at HQ
  7. Exclusive Use of Big Conference Room 2nd Floor HQ for 2 hours (subject to booking & availability)
  8. Exclusive Use of Crown Presidential Director Reserved Parking Bay at HQ (subject to availability)

Once again Congratulations! 

You have made it to the TOP at FE!
